      "writtenOn": "2018-08-16T22:02:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "no, this feature will be dropped. However, the problem that the feature used to solve no longer exist.\nYou can put large (\u003e1Kb) blobs into a property. It was a buildbot limitation.\n\nthere is chance that kitchen commandline will become too large on Windows. If that happens, we can fix that.",
