        "id": 1002882
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-08-16T22:18:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "As the findit variable builder is on Luci, we need to migrate away from additional_build_parameters. I think 1Kb might be enough. If needed, we could do some compression when passing over to the recipe.\n\nThe worse case is that a lot of tests or compile targets (could be object files instead of executables) fail consistently. That happened, but luckily it is rare.\n\nI filed https://crbug.com/875082",
      "parentUuid": "bb7bc6c0_9e102dfb",
